Notas utiles android
obtener permisos de superusuario
adb kill-server
adb start-server

instalar app
adb install /path/app.apk

reinstalar app
adb install -r /path/app.apk

uso de layouts sin xml

http://learn-it-stuff.blogspot.com/2011/12/creating-dynamic-layouts-in-android_18.html

capturar pantalla android via adb

adb shell screencap -p /sdcard/screen.png
adb pull /sdcard/screen.png
adb shell rm /sdcard/screen.png

http://blog.shvetsov.com/2013/02/grab-android-screenshot-to-computer-via.html
